snippet.title: Our Black Hole Video Is FAKE...? | Part-3
snippet.description:
We Are Not Claiming That We Make Real Black Hole, Obviously No One Can
But What We Made Is Also Looks Like Black Hole And Its Impressive. 

Watch Making Process - We Build Black Hole Making Machine -100% Real | Part-1 - https://youtu.be/91pe_U35C6U

Final Results - Finally !! We Create Black Hole Using Water | Part-2
Part-2 Link - https://youtu.be/z-d42gHvp5Y

Extra Shots - https://youtu.be/0KJhEZmK3C8

Why We Named This Black Hole ? Please Watch All These Videos For More Reference -
1 - https://youtu.be/kOnoYQchHFw
2 - https://youtu.be/XYiZW-j1ywc

No VFX Everything Is REAL Which You Will See In This Video.

Our Black Hole Making Machine use 40000 Liters Of Water To Operate.

Yes I Know This Is Not Real Black Hole Obviously, But Our Black Hole Also Has Some Similar Properties Which Real Black Hole Has Like Gravity, Accretion Disks etc.

A black hole is a region of spacetime where gravity is so strong that nothing, including light or other electromagnetic waves has enough energy to escape its event horizon. 

Our blackhole have also powerful gravity in the center and can pull a human size object inside the center.

If We Throw Any Object In The Machine They Start Orbiting The Black Hole Like The Galaxies, Stars Or Any Matter Orbit Real The Black Hole. And At The End Our Black Hole Can Also Sucks Everything That Comes On It's Way.

Love You All.
#mrindianhacker #blackhole

snippet.title: PLAYGROUND 2 AUCTION | @CarryMinati @triggeredinsaan, Scout, Ashish & Harsh Beniwal
snippet.description:
Playground is back! CarryMinati, Triggered Insaan, Ashish, ScoutOP & Harsh are trying to find the best contestants for the real money auction & pick them for their teams for the season starting 30th January streaming LIVE on YT & on Amazon miniTV! 

Voting lines for Super Subs open on Rumble, closes at 4:30 PM on 30th January. Vote here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robosoft.playverseStage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Auction rules*
• 40 contestants
• Only 28 will remain post auction
• 20 players, selected through bidding, will go directly into teams 
• 8 players will go into super subs
 • Of this, 5 players will be selected by the 5 mentors
 • And 3 players will be selected through voting on Rumble
• Player mix for teams - 1 Pro-player, 1 international player, Min. 1 player from previous season, Min. 1 female player
• Every week two players will get eliminated and new players will be selected from supers subs 
• 25L purse of each mentor to bid for players
• If a mentor has invoked an RTM card for a player during the Tryouts, they have the Right to Match the final bid on that player during the auction
• Mentors can retain players from their last season team, retained players will not be put up for auction, 35% of purse amount will be retention fee for retained player

snippet.title: (Ep-02) UPSC Aspirants किसी भी हाल में Vikas Sir की इन बातों को Miss मत करना 👆 | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह सही Skills, मेहनत, जज़्बे और जुनून के साथ करें अपना हर सपना सच: https://joshskills.app.link/YtNYUGvmVwb

अगर अभी तक Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की इस दिलचस्प, मज़ेदार और जानकारीपूर्ण सीरीज़ के Episode 01 को नहीं देखा तो अभी इस Link पर Click करें https://youtu.be/9lM79PRk_vA-

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 02 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. What has been the importance of Hindi and English Mediums in UPSC Results?
2. Online or Offline Education for UPSC Preparation, which is better?
3. What is Vikas Divyakirti Sir's opinion about the affordable and expensive UPSC Institutes?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. snippet.title: Nandamuri Taraka Ratna Health | Heart Attack Prevention | Myocardial Infarction | Manthena Official
snippet.description:
Nandamuri Taraka Ratna Health | Heart Attack Prevention | Myocardial Infarction | Manthena Official
----*-------*------

*This video is for Educational Purposes only* 
Viewers are advised not to use this information without any doctor's consultation

*ఈ వీడియో విద్యా ప్రయోజనాలు కోసం మాత్రమే చేయడం జరిగింది*  
- వీక్షకులు ఎటువంటి వైద్యుల సంప్రదింపులు లేకుండా ఈ సమాచారాన్ని ఉపయోగించవద్దని సూచన.

----*-------*------
డాక్టర్ మంతెన సత్యనారాయణ రాజు గారి ఆశ్రమం లో అనుభవజ్ఞులైన నేచురోపతి డాక్టర్లు ఏ ఆహారం తీసుకుంటే ఏ సమస్య పోతుందో తగు సలహాలు మరియు సూచనలు ఇస్తారు.

ఉదయం 7 గంటల నుండి రాత్రి 9 గంటల లోపు ఈ క్రింది ఫోన్ నెంబర్ కి ఎప్పుడైనా కాల్ చేసి మీ సమస్యలకు పరిష్కారం పొందవచ్చు.
9848021122. 

డాక్టర్ "మంతెన సత్యనారాయణ రాజు" గారి ఆశ్రమం లో వైద్య సేవల వివరాల కోసం, ఈ క్రింది ఫోన్ నెంబర్ కి కాల్ చేయండి.
08632333888.

Experienced naturopathic doctors will be available at Dr. Manthena Satyanarayana Raju Arogyalayam. They will give you advice on your problems.
Our Naturopath will suggest and indicate a proper diet plan based on your health problems.
You can call us at the below-given number anytime between 7 am and 9 pm to get advice on your issues. 9848021122.
For any queries regarding Dr. Manthena Satyanarayana Raju Ashramam, call the following phone number: 08632333888.

Are you sure? Don't want to miss any update from us...🙄 
If "Yes" 😉 Then immediately follow us on our social media...👇

Facebook 👉 https://www.facebook.com/DrManthenaOfficial
Instagram 👉 https://www.instagram.com/drmanthenaofficial/

Watch the all-new "Arogyame Mahayogam" Series in Zee Telugu Mon-Sat @ 8:30am

#nandamuritarakaratna #heartattack #ntr #koppam 

Healthy Recipes:
👉 ఉల్లిపాయ పకోడీ ఇలా చేసుకొని తినండి: https://youtu.be/OMqXY5szpTU
👉 హై ప్రోటీన్ సేమియా పాయసం చేసుకోండి ఇలా: https://youtu.be/PXGqoMPikRI
👉 వీటిని ఫ్రై చేసుకొని తినండి, బరువు తగ్గుతారు: https://youtu.be/IIu2vOlVR5o
👉 కాల్షియమ్ రిచ్ ఉప్మా: https://youtu.be/V3cL3Tt7J2U

Yoga With Tejaswini Manogna:
👉 ఇలా రెండు నిమిషాలు చేస్తే నడుము, సీటు భాగాల్లో కొవ్వు కరుగుతుంది: https://youtu.be/54UEg6Ky2Ys
👉 2 నిమిషాలు చేస్తే చాలు ఎంత పెద్ద పొట్టయినా కరిగిపోతుంది: https://youtu.be/mZtdFYcct2M
👉 ఉదయాన్నే ఈ రెండు చేస్తే, జుట్టు బాగా పెరుగుతుంది: https://youtu.be/J09INOyFuJk
👉 నేల పై పడుకుని ఇలా చేస్తే నడుము కొవ్వు కరుగుతుంది: https://youtu.be/UskLiJUM1Dg

Beauty Tips:
👉 రోజులో ఎప్పుడైనా ఒక గంట ఇలా చేయండి, జుట్టు తెల్లబడదు: https://youtu.be/dqWFzniOKUg
👉 ఈ పేస్ట్ మొఖానికి రాస్తే, స్కిన్ కలర్ మారుతుంది: https://youtu.be/PkgJnUJC9rE
👉 దీనిని రాత్రి వేళ ఇలా వాడితే, మొఖం పై నలుపు పోతుంది: https://youtu.be/lKDV9AoiKzs
👉 మీ జుట్టు వత్తుగా వేగంగా పెరగాలంటే: https://youtu.be/MAx1IPGmadw

Women Health:
👉 ఈ జ్యూస్ తాగితే, హార్మోన్ బాగా ఉత్పత్తి అవుతాయి: https://youtu.be/P6UCkMZKGvA
👉 రోజు మూడు నిముషాలు ఇలా చేస్తే, బరువు తగ్గుతారు: https://youtu.be/7BbJmuiOFnM
👉 పీరియడ్స్  రెగ్యులర్ గా అవటానికి : https://youtu.be/H4z0jHtf0sE
👉 PCOD ప్రాబ్లెమ్ తగ్గటానికి: https://youtu.be/pDgQsVXECW8

Weight Loss:
👉 బెండకాయ తింటే బరువు తగ్గుతారు, జ్ఞాపక శక్తి, మేధా శక్తి పెరుగుతాయి: https://youtu.be/sZ52FaVPAQk
👉 వెయిట్ లాస్ అవ్వాలన్న, పొట్ట కొవ్వు కారాగాలన్న పుల్కా ఎలా తినాలి? : https://youtu.be/67jejd9m3mg
👉 వారం లో ఒక రోజు ఇలా చేస్తే పొట్ట బరువు తగ్గి ఇమ్మ్యూనిటి బూస్ట్ అవుతుంది: https://youtu.be/-uiRVyX1K1w
👉 పెరుగు లో ఇది కలిపి తింటే ఎన్నో పోషకాలు: https://youtu.be/qVlBp5KuCXE

Health Tips:
👉 లావుగా ఉన్న వారు ఇంకా లావుగా కాకూడదంటే: https://youtu.be/6jEl6QcQ1X8
👉 వీటిని 2 చప్పున రోజు నోట్లో వేసుకోండి, లివర్ క్లీన్ అవుతుంది: https://youtu.be/d6gLDPgZ33E
👉 15 డేస్ లో స్పీడ్ గా వెయిట్ లాస్ అవ్వాలి అంటే: https://youtu.be/UJR14DWoXMA
👉 వారం లో 5 రోజులు దీన్ని తింటే, చెడు కొలెస్ట్రాల్ తగ్గుతుంది: https://youtu.be/FCXWvMmkrak

Naturopathy Lifestyle:
👉 దీన్ని ఇంత వాడి చూడండి, నీరసం మలబద్దకం పోతుంది: https://youtu.be/w8OkYdFmva4
👉 ఉదయాన్నే దీంట్లో ఈ పొడి వేసుకుని తాగితే, బరువు తగ్గుతారు: https://youtu.be/zOgefLTyvt4
👉 దీన్ని ఇంతే తినండి ఎక్కువ తిన్నారో, పేరాలసిస్ వస్తుంది: https://youtu.be/2PKOKN1sVcg
👉 గ్యాస్ ట్రబుల్ తగ్గి మీ పొట్ట ఫ్రీ గా అవ్వాలంటే: https://youtu.be/YFvJCluHbEk

Kavaa ton kathe hoke kalla ik baaj ni mareya 
Ajj tayi kade raaj nayi kita jungle vich moran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Maade jo time ch chad gaye kise nal harkh nayi koi 
Koi sanu ki samje painda hun fark ni koi 
Koi lakh kar jaye maada mathe kade vatt ni paya 
Pandita nu future de layi main nayi kade hath dikhaya 
Sach ni koi hoya aisa jo akhan ne biyan ni kareya 
Hoya ni saadh koi aisa rabb da jine dhayan ni dhareya 
Jinna vich uddeya firda saadh pune diya loran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Dheethan nal dheeth bade aa aunde kise guage ch haini 
Kimat meri puch ona ton jina di main range ch haini 
Chadar ton bahar kade vi nek na pair pasare 
Bolan di lod ni sanu paundi aa chupp khilare 
Sade te asar nayi kareya oh allarhan diyaan toran ne 
Vekhe kayi khunje laate jhanjar deya shoran ne 
Allarha impress karan layi na kaddiya kade tohra ne 
Dabde ni dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne

snippet.title: Sonam Wangchuk is fighting for Ladakh | Ladakh Protests Explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain why Sonam Wangchuk is protesting? What does Sonam Wangchuk and the rest of Ladakh wants from the government of India? And why Sonam Wangchuk was briefly under house arrest.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

Join us as we delve into the devastating impact of climate change on the beautiful region of Ladakh. From melting glaciers to changing weather patterns, this explainer video will highlight the current situation and its consequences on the local communities and their way of life. Watch now to understand how this remote corner of the world is affected and what can be done to mitigate the effects of global warming on Ladakh. #ClimateChange #Ladakh #sonamwangchuk

About Us:
Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. It was a way to change the way our negative feeds operated and replace negative news with positive, action-oriented news that made some change. They decode and simplify issues for Millenials and believe small steps lead to big outcomes in the future. Their videos span different genres like history, environment, and sustainability, policy discussions, social commentary, economics, personal finance, among others.

snippet.title: Adani Group - Hindenburg: LIC, SBI-க்கு பாதிப்பா? - அதானி எதிர்காலம் என்னவாகும்?Explained
snippet.description:
அமெரிக்காவைச் சேர்ந்த ஹிண்டன்பர்க் ஆய்வு நிறுவனம் வெளியிட்ட ஆய்வறிக்கை, அதானி குழுமத்தையே அசைத்திருக்கிறது.  இந்த ஆய்வறிக்கை என்ன கூறுகிறது, இதற்கு அதானி குழுமம் கூறும் பதில் என்ன, அதானி குழுமத்தில் முதலீடு செய்திருப்பவர்களுக்கு ஏதேனும் ஆபத்தா, எஸ்.பி.ஐ. போன்ற வங்கிகளுக்கும், எல்.ஐ.சி.க்கும் பாதிப்பு ஏற்பட வாய்ப்பிருக்கிறதா என்பது பற்றி இந்தக் காணொளியில் பார்க்கலாம்.

#AdaniGroup #Hindenburg #StockMarket #LIC #SBI

snippet.title: MAAN MERI JAAN SUPREMACY I KING AFTER-PARTY INDIA TOUR AFTERMOVIE TEASER
snippet.description:
#MaanMeriJaan #ChampagneTalk #King 

In October 2023, I presented my 3rd Studio Album Champagne Talk to the World. We also set out on a Tour across 18 cities the very next day to celebrate the album with you. 

Hyderabad-Pune-Indore-Mumbai-Vadodara-Ludhiana-Nagpur-Kolkata-Delhi-Jaipur-Ahmedabad-Bengaluru-Ranchi-Delhi-Kolkata-Guwahati-Surat-Goa
And the one song that roared across the nation was Maan Meri Jaan.

It’s not possible to put into words the Magic we experienced. You all came together to make my biggest dream come true. And to prove that Kingsclan is not just a word. It’s an emotion we all feel. Together. 

Thank you for the Phenomenon. Thank you for creating the Term of the year – Maan Meri Jaan Supremacy. And thank you for being there. 

Special Thanks to Team Innovation for amazing Tour partners. 
TOUR AFTERMOVIE DROPS ON 5TH FEBRUARY. STAY TUNED

FEATURES :
Arpan Kumar Chandel aka King
Section 8 : Dj
Dan Thomas : Drums
Birraj K Taneja : Keys
Shubanshu Singh : Guitar
Danik Ghosh : Bass Guitar
Hanish Taneja : Sound Engineer & SFX
Additional Sound Team : Piyush 
Amey Pendarkar : Lights Engineer
Harsh Patel : Visual Engineer

Hyderabad-Pune-Indore-Mumbai-Vadodara-Ludhiana-Nagpur-Kolkata-Delhi-Jaipur-Ahmedabad-Bengaluru-Ranchi-Delhi-Kolkata-Guwahati-Surat-Goa

#RepublicDay Parade 2023 का सीधा प्रसारण | 26 January Parade Live #RepublicDayparade #RepublicDay2023 #IndiaRepublicDay #गणतंत्रदिवस India celebrates her 74th Republic Day on 26 January 2023. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

snippet.title: Hindunberg ने फिर से Adani की रिपोर्ट पर क्या कहा?
snippet.description:
#adani #hindenburg #adanigroup #report #adanipower #adanienterprises #research 
हिंडनबर्ग ने कहा है कि अडानी ग्रुप राष्ट्रवाद का चोला ओढ़ रहा है. सोमवार को दिए गए स्पष्ट्रीकरण ने फर्म ने अडानी ग्रुप पर आरोप लगाते हुए कहा कि अडानी ग्रुप ने अभी भी उसके सवालों का जवाब नहीं दिया है
बिजनेस जगत की हर बड़ी खबर, उनसे जुड़े एक्सप्लेनर वीडियो, बिजनेस शख्सियत  की दिलचस्प कहानियां, रियल एस्टेट, गोल्ड, ऑटो सेक्टर, स्टार्टअप्स,  शेयर बाजार, सेंसेक्स और पर्सलन फाइनेंस जैसे विषयों की जानकारी हासिल करने के लिए जुड़े बिजनेस टुडे हिंदी से। यहां आपकों म्यूचुअल फंड, एसआईपी, इक्विटी, बीमा, लोन्स, पेंशन, रिटायरमेंट योजनाओं के बारे में आसान भाषा में मिलेगी दिलचस्प जानकारी।

snippet.title: Dr. Vikas Divyakirti Sir क्यों बोले '1 भी बात गलत हुई तो मैं ज़िम्मेदार हूं' 🤔 | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह अपने Skills, मेहनत, ज़िद और जुनून के दम पर बनें Successful :https://joshskills.app.link/4iaNjbgiVwb

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 01 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. Why Vikas Sir's surname is Dvyakirti?
2. What was his UPSC Exam Result?

snippet.title: Thapki ने किया Shraddha को ब्लैकमेल | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 608
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Thapki gathers evidence against Shraddha by recording her confessions. She blackmails Shraddha into handing over the legal papers in exchange for the recordings. Will Shraddha comply with Thapki's demands?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.description:
The Theatrical Trailer of the Bittersweet Tale of Adolescence and love, #ButtaBomma is here! 💌  In Cinemas 4th Feb 2023!

Here's the #ButtaBomma Official Teaser! Butta Bomma is a upcoming telugu film, featuring Anikha Surendran, Arjun Das, Surya Vashistta, Navya Swamy in lead roles, Music by Gopi Sundar and film directed by Shouree Chandrashekhar T Ramesh. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya under Sithara Entertainments in Association with Fortune Four Cinemas.

snippet.title: Bharat Jodo Yatra में Rahul Gandhi का माथा चूमती दिखी Mehbooba Mufti की मां Gulshan Begum | Congress
snippet.description:
Bharat Jodo Yatra में Rahul Gandhi का माथा चूमती दिखी Mehbooba Mufti की मां Gulshan Begum | Congress

#livehindustan #rahulgandhi #bharatjodoyatra 

राहुल गांधी की भारत जोड़ो यात्रा कश्मीर में चल रही है, श्रीनगर के लाल चौक पर 30 जनवरी को इसका समापन होना है, आखिरी कुछ दिनों में भारत जोड़ो यात्रा में जबरदस्त जोश देखने को मिल रहा है, शनिवार को भी राहुल गांधी की पदयात्रा में भीषण ठंड के बाद भी  बड़ी संख्या में स्थानीय लोग भी यात्रा से जुड़े, यात्रा के दौरान पूर्व मुख्यमंत्री महबूबा मुफ्ती बेटी इल्तिजा मुफ्ती भी शामिल हुई, इस दौरान महबूबा मुफ्ती की मां गुलशन बेगम ने राहुल गांधी का माथा चुमा जिसका वीडियो वायरल हो गया है।

Mehbooba Mufti Mother Gulshan Begum Kisses Rahul Gandhi See Pics Of Her Daughter Iltija Congress Bharat Jodo Yatra In Kashmir

#RepublicDay Parade 2023 का सीधा प्रसारण | 26 January Parade Live #RepublicDayparade #RepublicDay2023 #IndiaRepublicDay #गणतंत्रदिवस India celebrates her 74th Republic Day on 26 January 2023. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan. 

#IndianRepublicDay2023 #RepublicDayFullParade #IndianArmy #IndiacelebratesRepublicDay #RepublicDaycelebrations #IndianNationalFlag #GantantraDivasParade #HappyRepublicDay #RepublicDay2023 #74thRepublicDay #RepublicDayParade2023 #EgyptPresident Abdel Fattah al-Sisi  #DroupadiMurmu
#PMModi #AmarJawanJyoti #PatrioticVideo #BikestuntsbyIndianArmy #NarendraModi #DDNational #DoordarshanLIVE #Rajpath #IndiaGate #MinistryofDefence #RepublicDay #WarMemorial

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 10 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: SYAAPA : EP 02 | LADKI KA CHAKAR | COMEDY | KANGRA BOYS 2023
snippet.description:
"SYAAPA" is Himachal's First Ever web series produced by KANGRA BOYS

"SYAAPA" is the story of four friends and one of their senior advocate Makkhan. In this episode all four friends after being expelled from their college return to their ancestral house in their village. Here they encounter a dead body in their house and all of them are haunted by the fear that they might be accused of his murder. Now, they call one of their college senior advocate Makhan for help. Let's see how these four friends deal with this problem and if advocate Makkhan comes to help them.      

Cast: Rajat Dogra, Sachin Dogra, Puneet Suman, Avraaj Kumar, Arvind Kumar,Gulzar Thukral, Swati Sharma, Shikha Sadwal, Prateeksha Thakur, Akhil Chaudhary , H.S. snippet.title: भारत पहुंचने वाले है 40 टन  के दो पत्थर, रोने लगे हज़ारो लोग | India waits for Black stones |
snippet.description:
Black stones known as “shaligram shila” from the Kali Gandaki river in Nepal will reach Ayodhya for the carving of Lord Ram’s idol in the inner sanctum of the Ram Mandir being built in the city that Hindus believe is the birthplace of the hero of Ramayana, people aware of the matter said.

नेपाल से दो विशाल शालिग्राम शिलाएं अयोध्या लाई जा रही हैं. इनसे श्रीराम और माता सीता की मूर्ति बनाई जाएंगी. दावा है कि ये शिलाएं करीब 6 करोड़ साल पुरानी हैं. हालांकि, इनसे बनी मूर्तियां गर्भगृह में रखी जाएंगी या परिसर में कहीं और स्थापित होगी? ये अभी तय नहीं है.

#ZeeOriginals #RamMandir #Ayodhya

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 09 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 09 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 25th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

Bushra Ansari as Salma

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Sadhguru X Kamiya Jani | Sunday Brunch EP 95 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this episode of Sunday Brunch we caught up with the spiritual leader, Sadhguru at Isha Yoga Center, Coimbatore. He is the founder and head of the Isha Foundation, an ashram and yoga center.

In this chat, he got candid about his childhood, education, homeschooling, and spirituality. He opened up about his love for motorbikes and golf. 


He takes us through a day in his life and advises us on eating habits we all should follow for healthier living. 


We hope you enjoy watching the video and gain some encouraging advice to lead a healthy and positive life.

snippet.description:

ख़रीदिए कारवाँ मोबाइल- 1500 प्रीलोडिड गानों वाला कीपैड फ़ोन धमाकेदार साउंड के साथ

Credits:

Song Name :  Murugiya Tasli Me Bani

Mama sukha sukhi aai kaise aaj
M/ aara se aai Sara log khai sabh ke bhetayi tani tani
E Holi asli me mani murugiya tasali me bani
1Antra/
F/ Holi ke mahaul pura garam bhayil ba
Aaj ta busy murgi faram bhayil ba
M/ ta chinta na kara hamar maina
Ham ta pahile se de dele bani baina
M/ Kara na hala laim garam masala
Dhani jhora liyawa chahe panni
E Holi asli me mani murugiya tasali me bani
2antra/
F/ Krishna bedardi khesari ho
Aaj nahi bani tarkari ho
M/ leke aawtani chulha garmaile raha
Silwati pa lodhwa dhaile raha
M/ Hoi dhur khel Jani hoiha ha tu fel Kami Masti me hoi na chawanni
E Holi asli me mani murugiya tasali me bani

snippet.title: Shraddha के ख़िलाफ़ खड़ी हुईं Thapki | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 607
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Thapki finds out that Shraddha had blackmailed Tina to request Bihaan to get married to Sankar. Thapki decides put a stop to Shraddha's atrocities. But will she be successful?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3680 - 28 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3680: Taarak's Green Shirt
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal and Taarak make their way to his office. Champaklal becomes unsure about the alibi, which Taarak can inform his boss about. Meanwhile, Taarak's boss video calls him, but he is afraid to answer because he is now wearing a green shirt instead of a yellow one. Champaklal suggests that Taarak make a normal phone call to his boss in order to conceal the truth about the shirt. Everyone in the office is wearing yellow shirts, and Taarak is expected to wear one as well. What happens when he sees Taarak dressed in a green shirt instead? Will Champaklal's cover-up save Taarak? Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3680, 28 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000207527

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

snippet.title: Lallantop के कैमरे पर Rahul ने Lal Chowk पर तिरंगा फहराया, तो आम कश्मीरियों ने क्या कहा?
snippet.description:
On January 29th, Rahul Gandhi reached Lal Chowk to hoist the tricolor flag. Bharat Jodo Yatra is about to end in Kashmir via Kanyakumari, before that Rahul Gandhi hoisted the tricolor flag, what happened while hoisting the flag? What was the number of common Kashmiris present there? What did they said about the Bharat Jodo Yatra? And what did Congress leaders Imran Pratapgarhi, Deepender Hooda and Jitu Patwari present there said? To know watch this report of Abhinav Pandey.
